## 14. Testing

### Current Tests
- `tests/TestSaveManager.cpp` - Save/Load round-trip, slot isolation, delete slot, missing key tolerance, summary, autosave
- `tests/TestMergeController.cpp` - Merge timing buckets, lock expiry, forced merge, voluntary gate, climax hold
- `tests/TestStorySequencer.cpp` - Beat table structure, scene names, event flow
- `tests/TestGotchiSim.cpp` - Simulation reducer logic
- `tests/TestGrimeShader.cpp` - Grime shader functionality

### Test Execution
```bash
./tests/TestMergeController
./tests/TestStorySequencer
./tests/TestSaveManager
```

