## 15. Key Constants

| Constant | Value | Description |
|----------|-------|-------------|
| `GAME_W` | 720 | Game width (pixels) |
| `GAME_H` | 720 | Game height (pixels) |
| `GOTCHI_TICK_RATE` | 1.0s | Base tick interval |
| `SAVE_VERSION` | 1 | Current save format version |
| `NUM_SLOTS` | 3 | Number of save slots |
| `SLEEP_DRAIN_RATE` | 0.02/s | Sleep drain during gotchi mode |
| `MERGE_LOCK_COOLDOWN_SEC` | 3.0 | Button lock after each beat |
| `AFFECTION_GAIN` | 0.08 | Per warmth action |
| `MERCY_GAIN` | 0.12 | Per hygiene action |
| `GRIME_CREEP_RATE` | 0.01/s | Grime increase during neglect |
| `COLLAPSE_NEED_THRESHOLD` | 0.05 | Need level that triggers collapse |

